Subject: wifi: ath11k: drop PCIe PME capability for IPQ9574 AHB

IPQ9574 uses the integrated AHB Wi-Fi path. Do not advertise the PCIe
PME D3cold host capability to its WLFW service.

Signed-off-by: Igor Kravchenko <igor.kravchenko05@gmail.com>
---
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/qmi.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/qmi.c
@@ -1757,7 +1757,8 @@ int ath11k_qmi_host_cap_send(struct ath1
 	if (ab->hw_params.global_reset)
 		req.nm_modem |= PLATFORM_CAP_PCIE_GLOBAL_RESET;
 
-	req.nm_modem |= PLATFORM_CAP_PCIE_PME_D3COLD;
+	if (ab->hw_rev != ATH11K_HW_IPQ9574)
+		req.nm_modem |= PLATFORM_CAP_PCIE_PME_D3COLD;
 
 	ath11k_dbg(ab, ATH11K_DBG_QMI, "host cap request\n");
 
